type.description: The type of the event, always `image_gen.partial_image`.

sequence_number.description: The sequence number of the event that was emitted.

partial_image_index.description: The index of the partial image that was emitted.

b64_json.description: The base64-encoded partial image that was emitted.

created_at.description: The timestamp when the partial image was created.

size.description: The image size that was used.

quality.description: The image quality that was used.

background.description: The background setting that was used.

output_format.description: The output format that was used.

title: Image generation partial image event
description: A streaming event that indicated a partial image was emitted during image generation.
